Title: Relates to management, development, and funding of the commercial shellfish aquaculture industry
Summary: Relates to the management, development, and funding of the commercial shellfish aquaculture industry; establishes a director of aquacultural and maricultural resources position in the department of agriculture and markets.
LawCode: Amd §16, Ag & Mkts L; amd §§13-0105 & 13-0350, En Con L; amd §83, St Fin L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law, the environmental conservation law, and the state finance law, in relation to management and development of the commercial shellfish aquaculture industry
